{"title":"钢铁","authors":["刘昌庆　李丹平"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":4,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘昌庆　李丹平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八十年前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群钢筋铁骨的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把镰刀和斧头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"论证在一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自此，中国开始领悟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要锻造这些开创"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英特纳雄耐尔的工具"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"需要大批的特殊材料"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——钢铁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点燃起信念的熔炉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冶炼浇铸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈大山里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一批优质矿石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遵义锤炼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延安成型"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜血淬火的钢铁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚硬　乌亮　铮铮有声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇铸五颗金星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘扬成共和国的风采"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又以犁铧的姿势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在解冻的田垄上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种五谷阳光和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及先进的生产力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历经磨砺的钢铁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于磨成一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比自身更硬的箴言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发展是硬道理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们沿长江三峡的大坝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿大京九机车的轰鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿西部大开发的路轨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰轰隆隆碾压落后与贫穷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一个雄鸡形的版图上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍植民族的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文明与富裕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁的大船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘风破浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥抱新世纪的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶风冒雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向新的高度飞翔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁的脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺就中国新的跑道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在英雄的诗史上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写下第三代的足迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"著名的钢铁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象征着一种高贵的品质"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的成色远在黄金之上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少年过去了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们开始寻找一种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更深层的意义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"譬如人民利益"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"譬如先进文化和先进生产力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让它辉煌成一种圣火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作为航标"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在历史关头托起使命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾驭着一个时代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起落多变的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潮潮汐汐"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}